title: Helicopter Strike Force
description:
Fully destructible 3D environment / 18 combat missions with
multiple objectives / Multiplayer mode online or over a
network / ESRB Rating T Teen

Take the controls of a combat helicopter, push it to the limit
to protect the island peoples from the corrupt El Presidente
and his forces. With it fully destructible 3D environment
enemies as well as friends can be destroyed. Youll get plenty
of replay with 18 combat missions, many of which have multiple
objectives. Clash with others online or over a Network in
helicopter-vs-helicopter battle to find out who is the best
helicopter pilot

Fully destructible 3D environment--enemies as well as friends
can be destroyed

18 combat missions many missions have multiple objectives

Thorough storyline to lead you from one mission to the next

Fast-paced action with intuitive and fluid gameplay

Numerous weapon options

Multiplayer mode--clash with others online or over a network
in
helicopter-vs-helicopter battle to find out who is the best
helicopter pilot

Windows Vista / XP
